The evidence with the title 'Like obamacare, Trumpcare offers immediate subsidies -- for more ... ' says Mar 8, 2017  ... Healthcare analysts feared the replacement bill would make people pay their full premiums every month and not get their subsidies until after filing tax returns  ... Earning $ 80,000 a year -- and ineligible for any Obamacare subsidies because of their income -- could get an $ 8,000 subsidy under Trumpcare . 
